---
title: Honey Butter–Glazed Chicken with Smoky Potato Salad & Roasted Broccoli
description: Pork just loves a sweet sauce, and this simple honey-butter glaze is just the thing for bringing these tender boneless chops to the next level. We’re serving them with a big helping of creamy, tangy potato salad (livened up with zingy mustard and crisp scallions) to bring the cookout vibes, plus a side of roasted salt-and-pepper broccoli to round things out. It’s a meat and potatoes meal that's quick to the table, and quick to satisfy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66019a2ada283ecbc2883ce8-efb4a679.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/660452eee705429b0f6ac798.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 660 kcal
  fat: 30 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 57 g
  sugar: 22 g
